        <item>
            <title>Counter-Strike 2 防作弊機制有問題　與 AMD 驅動程式不相容</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/14/amd-gpu-driver-trigger-vac-bans-in-counter-strike-2/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=amd-gpu-driver-trigger-vac-bans-in-counter-strike-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/14/amd-gpu-driver-trigger-vac-bans-in-counter-strike-2/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 15:11:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AMD]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Counter-strike 2]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199351</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>現在不少遊戲都有防作弊機制，不過有時候卻會帶來不便。最近 Valve 表示，AMD 顯示卡的最新驅動程式會觸發這個系統，導致遊戲無法正常遊玩。<br /><span id="more-1199351"></span></p><p>Valve 在公告中表示，AMD 顯示卡驅動程式的 Anti-Lag+ 功能雖然可以減低遲延，不過由於其運作原理是截取和重新導向 DLL（動態連結庫）函數，Counter-Strike 2 的放作弊系統會將其視為作弊而被封鎖。Valve 表示要解決問題，仍然有待 AMD 方面推出更新修復問題，他們就會撤銷對受影響玩家的禁令。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">AMD&#39;s latest driver has made their &quot;Anti-Lag/+&quot; feature available for CS2, which is implemented by detouring engine dll functions.</p><p>If you are an AMD customer and play CS2, DO NOT ENABLE ANTI-LAG/+; any tampering with CS code will result in a VAC ban.</p><p>Once AMD ships an update we…</p><p>&mdash; CS2 (@CounterStrike) <a href="https://twitter.com/CounterStrike/status/1712875606776729832?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 13, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>如果正在使用 AMD 顯示卡，可以在設定中關閉 Anti-Lag+ 功能，或者用 Alt+L 快捷鍵關閉功能，才開始玩 Counter-Strike 2 就最為安全。這事件也引起一些用家不滿，認為防作弊功能對真正作弊的玩家起不了作用，反而對一般玩家造成麻煩。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/GlobalOffensive/comments/1770slx/warning_recent_amd_gpu_driver_update_23101_may/">Reddit</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
