        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple 製作伴讀影片，推廣 Pomodoro 溫習法</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/14/apple-study-with-me-pomodoro/notebook/mac-os/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-study-with-me-pomodoro</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/14/apple-study-with-me-pomodoro/notebook/mac-os/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 22:37:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活學習]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[macbook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pomodoro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Study with Me]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199278</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前 Apple 在官方 YouTube 頻道上載影片「Study With Me」，這是一段宣傳以 Mac 輔助學習的影片。有別於一般產品推廣廣告短片，今次「Study With Me」的片長達 1.5 小時，而且片中並沒有任何有關 Mac 的介紹。與其説是產品宣傳，不如説成是「伴讀」影片。</p><p><span id="more-1199278"></span></p><p>「Study With Me」由荷里活女星 Storm Reid 主持，她同時是南加州大學的學生，在影片中 Reid 會分享如何以 Pomodoro（番茄鐘）技巧去進行 1.5 小時的溫習。短片分成 3 段 25 小時的專注溫習時間，期間再夾雜 3 段 5 分鐘的休息放鬆時間。「Study With Me」會提供適合專注溫習的 Lo-Fi 背景音樂，而休息期間 Reid 則會分享她的心得，例如進食小食、舒展身體和聽歌跳舞。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_92171"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ti6r17_TWf4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>有興趣試試 Pomodoro 方式的人，可以一邊播放「Study With Me」影片，一邊開始溫習或工作。Apple 在影片資訊欄中提到 Reid 所使用的筆電是 15 吋 MacBook Air，標榜配備 M2 處理器，具備多工作業能力和 18 小時電池續航力。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：Apple</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_15922"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ti6r17_TWf4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
